{"tid":2450082,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"40歲女星私照曝光！真實皮膚狀態驚呆網　驚呼：不可能","createTime":"2021-03-17T06:36:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T11:55:45.000Z","uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"18e23fb9e41bdd5e1faa50a6b3ae6f85f2300466","tid":2450082,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T06:36:01.000Z","msg":"現代保養方式多元，不少人靠著先天條件和後天的努力保有童顏，不說可能都猜不出來幾歲，韓國演員張娜拉就是如此。4月將推出新戲劇作品的她時常在IG上更新自己的照片，和真實年齡差超多的凍齡美照讓大家都相當驚訝。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/03/17/3068614-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F03%2F17%2F3068614-PH.jpg&h=5b305f74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲張娜拉戲劇作品相當受歡迎，童顏外貌也備受討論。（圖／翻攝自張娜拉IG）<br />\n<br />\n張娜拉出道將滿20年，從歌手轉型成演員的她戲劇作品相當受歡迎，包括翻拍台劇的「命中注定我愛你」、曾引起一陣追劇旋風的「皇后的品格」等等，讓她成功躋身一線演員，除了戲劇作品，她超級童顏的外表也為人津津樂道，3月18日將迎來40歲生日的她，照片看起來仍然超像學生。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/03/17/3068612-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F03%2F17%2F3068612-PH.jpg&h=b3859537&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲張娜拉（中）即將滿40歲，粉絲大喊看不出來。（圖／翻攝自張娜拉IG）<br />\n<br />\n從幾張張娜拉在IG上分享的照片可以看到，她的皮膚狀態還是相當好，過年時也曝光休閒照和粉絲們拜年，只見她穿著一件白色連帽外套，戴上帽子向鏡頭露出甜美笑容，活潑模樣就像學生，讓粉絲們大感驚艷。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/03/17/3068613-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F03%2F17%2F3068613-PH.jpg&h=720b4af7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲張娜拉穿起連帽外套就像學生。（圖／翻攝自張娜拉IG）<br />\n<br />\n而張娜拉也在4月將上檔的新劇《大發不動產》中飾演社長兼驅魔師的角色，先前也自己曝光過花絮照，官方也分享了劇照，只見她穿上一身俐落的西裝，成熟美大爆發，但也不抵她童顏的臉龐，吸引不少網友留言讚美「太期待了」、「姐姐好美」、「也太可愛了」、「姐姐最可愛！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/03/17/3068620-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F03%2F17%2F3068620-PH.jpg&h=9c77fe06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲張娜拉在新戲中的造型展現成熟美。（圖／翻攝自KBS drama IG）"},{"pid":"c7f80dcdfacd2bd908a4a4327ac59267f11066f8","tid":2450082,"uid":175070,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T06:40:45.000Z","msg":"仲要好戲果下先勁"},{"pid":"634aa7e2e2e309ae10e1cb01916586aef4807496","tid":2450082,"uid":339805,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T06:42:37.000Z","msg":"老女人不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be206af3c45e8f5174cf68496bb590cfd63f31b9","tid":2450082,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T06:42:53.000Z","msg":"塊面太扁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f89492f2cb8cbb37d02b4c2fc4bc3e0d2a3739a0","tid":2450082,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"634aa7e2e2e309ae10e1cb01916586aef4807496","tid":2450082,"uid":339805,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T06:42:37.000Z","msg":"老女人不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T06:43:05.000Z","msg":"你老男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d9b4b0237f222ec46c78cfdfee7cdb91da04b04","tid":2450082,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f89492f2cb8cbb37d02b4c2fc4bc3e0d2a3739a0","tid":2450082,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"634aa7e2e2e309ae10e1cb01916586aef4807496","tid":2450082,"uid":339805,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T06:42:37.000Z","msg":"老女人不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T06:43:05.000Z","msg":"你老男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T06:44:10.000Z","msg":"我2020出世<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9322fd1fccaa8c3830a5fad8c73a5c4a493addeb","tid":2450082,"uid":323740,"like":0,"disl